These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, teacher, chef, analyst, doctor, project-manager, dressmaker
There are 7 different nationalities: french, dutch, russian, malaysian, italian, pakistani, american
 1. the analyst is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the italian is the analyst##1
 3. the dressmaker is on the right of the project-manager##1
 4. the russian is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the chef is in the middle##1
 6. the french is on the far left##1
 7. the doctor is the french##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the pakistani##1
 9. the russian is on the left of the dutch##1
10. the malaysian is on the left of the chef##1
11. the dressmaker is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | doctor | analyst | teacher | chef | freelancer | project-manager | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | french    | italian   | malaysian      | pakistani | russian    | dutch    | american         |

