.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cherry, pear, grapefruit, pumpkin, kiwi, corn, garlic
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, folk, electronic, ambient, indie, trance
 1. the fan of ambient is the person eating pumpkin##1
 2. the person eating corn is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating pear is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 7. the fan of ambient is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the fan of trance is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cherry | pear | kiwi | pumpkin | corn | garlic | grapefruit |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | folk   | electronic   | ambient      | hip-hop       | trance       | indie     |

