.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: zucchini, tomato, strawberry, broccoli, grapefruit, mango, cabbage
The people have 7 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, pilot, dressmaker, doctor, police-officer, architect
 1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the architect##1
 3. the manager is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 5. the lawyer is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the pilot is on the right of the manager##1
 7. the manager is on the left of the pilot##1
 8. the manager is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 9. the person eating mango is the dressmaker##1
10. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the lawyer##1
11. the dressmaker is in the middle##1
12. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | tomato | grapefruit     | strawberry  | mango       | zucchini       | cabbage  | broccoli   |
| Job    | police-officer  | lawyer | architect | dressmaker | manager | pilot | doctor |

