.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, trance, house, country, pop, classical
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish, mexican, italian, german, dutch, colombian
 1. the fan of country is the spanish##1
 2. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 3. the dutch is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
 7. the mexican is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the right of the dutch##1
 9. the fan of trance is the german##1
10. the german is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
11. the colombian is the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | classical     | house     | trance      | d&b | country      | ambient     |
| Nationality   | italian | mexican | dutch | german | colombian | spanish | brazilian |

