.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: traveling, singing, skydiving, reading, collecting, chess, woodworking
7 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, rabbit, hedgehog, rat, mouse, ferret
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | chess     | reading | woodworking | collecting | traveling |
| Pet     | ferret   | rabbit    | rat | mouse     | lizard         | hedgehog     | cat        |

