.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, tea, lemonade, water, hot-chocolate, cola
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, boat, airplane, van, scooter, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person drinking milk is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | tea | hot-chocolate   | milk | lemonade | cola  | water | fanta |
| Transport   | airplane   | van | helicopter | scooter     | subway | snowmobile | boat   |

