.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, family, superhero, mystery, epic, documentary, sports
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, quad-bike, tram, scooter, van, car
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | sports | mystery | epic | documentary     | family | superhero |
| Transport     | van | tram      | car | quad-bike    | scooter | airplane   | helicopter  |

