 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1

